          <li>From time to time, it is necessary for customers to supply us with data in connection with the opening or continuation of accounts and the establishment or continuation of facilities or provision of services or compliance with any laws or guidelines issued by regulatory or other authorities.</li>
          <li>Failure to supply such data may result in BITFINEX being unable to open or continue accounts or establish or continue facilities or provide services or comply with any laws or guidelines issued by regulatory or other authorities.</li>
          <li>It is also the case that data are collected from customers in the ordinary course of the continuation of the relationship (for example in case the guidelines change).</li>
